---
// Prizes section with actual COCHATECH 2026 prize content
---

<section id="premios" class="prizes-section">
  <div class="prizes-container">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="prizes-header" data-animate>
      <h2 class="prizes-title">
        <span class="prizes-accent">Premios</span> y Reconocimiento
      </h2>
      <p class="prizes-text">
        COCHATECH 2026 no solo premia proyectos — abre puertas reales al ecosistema tech de Bolivia y el mundo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Gran Premio: Silicon Valley -->
    <div class="prizes-featured" data-animate data-animate-delay="100">
      <div class="prizes-featured-content">
        <div class="prizes-featured-left">
          <div class="prizes-featured-icon" aria-hidden="true">✈️</div>
          <h3 class="prizes-featured-title">El Gran Premio: ¡Rumbo a Silicon Valley!</h3>
          <p class="prizes-featured-description">
            El equipo con la solución de mayor impacto y viabilidad técnica obtiene el pase directo a la meca de la tecnología mundial.
          </p>
          <ul class="prizes-benefits-list">
            <li class="prizes-benefit-item">
              <span class="prizes-benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚡</span>
              <span class="prizes-benefit-text">Fast-Track a Antigravity (Cohort 4): entrevista directa al prestigioso programa Puentes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="prizes-benefit-item">
              <span class="prizes-benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏙️</span>
              <span class="prizes-benefit-text">La Experiencia "Puentes": programa inmersivo de una semana completa en San Francisco, California</span>
            </li>
            <li class="prizes-benefit-item">
              <span class="prizes-benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏠</span>
              <span class="prizes-benefit-text">10 desarrolladores conviviendo en mansión exclusiva, frente a frente con empresas, inversores y startups de Silicon Valley</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="prizes-featured-right">
          <span class="prizes-value-label">Hito histórico para Bolivia</span>
          <div class="prizes-value-display">Silicon<br/>Valley</div>
          <div class="prizes-badges">
            <span class="ds-badge ds-badge-yellow">
              <span class="ds-badge-dot ds-badge-dot-yellow" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              Antigravity Cohort 4
            </span>
            <span class="ds-badge ds-badge-outline">
              <span class="ds-badge-dot ds-badge-dot-cyan" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              San Francisco, CA
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="prizes-featured-credit">
            Posible gracias a las gestiones estratégicas de <strong>Gadi Borovich</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Premios por Categoría -->
    <div class="prizes-categories-section">
      <div class="prizes-categories-header" data-animate>
        <h3 class="prizes-categories-title">🏆 Premios por Categoría</h3>
        <span class="ds-badge ds-badge-outline">
          <span class="ds-badge-dot ds-badge-dot-cyan" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Fintech · Social · Empresarial
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="prizes-categories-subtitle" data-animate>
        Para los equipos ganadores en cada una de las tres líneas de acción:
      </p>

      <div class="prizes-grid">
        <div class="prizes-card" data-animate data-animate-delay="0">
          <div class="prizes-card-icon prizes-icon-cyan" aria-hidden="true">☁️</div>
          <h4 class="prizes-card-title">Infraestructura Cloud</h4>
          <p class="prizes-card-text">
            Créditos de Amazon Web Services para alojar, probar y escalar sus soluciones tecnológicas en la nube.
          </p>
          <div class="prizes-card-reward prizes-text-cyan">$1,000 USD en créditos AWS</div>
        </div>

        <div class="prizes-card" data-animate data-animate-delay="80">
          <div class="prizes-card-icon prizes-icon-yellow" aria-hidden="true">💰</div>
          <h4 class="prizes-card-title">Capital en Especie</h4>
          <p class="prizes-card-text">
            Herramientas o insumos para seguir desarrollando sus proyectos.
          </p>
          <div class="prizes-card-reward prizes-text-yellow">1,000 – 2,000 Bs. en premios</div>
        </div>

        <div class="prizes-card" data-animate data-animate-delay="160">
          <div class="prizes-card-icon prizes-icon-cyan" aria-hidden="true">🎓</div>
          <h4 class="prizes-card-title">Actualización Tecnológica</h4>
          <p class="prizes-card-text">
            Medias becas para cursos y programas especializados en Automatización.
          </p>
          <div class="prizes-card-reward prizes-text-cyan">Becas de capacitación</div>
        </div>

        <div class="prizes-card" data-animate data-animate-delay="240">
          <div class="prizes-card-icon prizes-icon-white" aria-hidden="true">🌐</div>
          <h4 class="prizes-card-title">Inmersión Web3</h4>
          <p class="prizes-card-text">
            Creación y gestión de "Perfiles Profesionales Cripto" para proyectar el talento hacia la economía digital global.
          </p>
          <div class="prizes-card-reward prizes-text-white">Perfil en ecosistema global</div>
        </div>

        <div class="prizes-card" data-animate data-animate-delay="320">
          <div class="prizes-card-icon prizes-icon-cyan" aria-hidden="true">🎁</div>
          <h4 class="prizes-card-title">Kits del Ecosistema</h4>
          <p class="prizes-card-text">
            Souvenirs y paquetes exclusivos otorgados por aliados estratégicos: Banca, ONGs, Empresas y el Municipio de Cochabamba.
          </p>
          <div class="prizes-card-reward prizes-text-cyan">Paquetes exclusivos de aliados</div>
        </div>

        <div class="prizes-card" data-animate data-animate-delay="400">
          <div class="prizes-card-icon prizes-icon-yellow" aria-hidden="true">🎊</div>
          <h4 class="prizes-card-title">Reconocimiento Corporativo</h4>
          <p class="prizes-card-text">
            Cajas de sorpresas exclusivas armadas directamente por las organizaciones retadoras.
          </p>
          <div class="prizes-card-reward prizes-text-yellow">Sorpresas de las empresas</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Premios de Empleabilidad -->
    <div class="prizes-employment-section" data-animate>
      <div class="prizes-employment-header">
        <div class="prizes-employment-icon" aria-hidden="true">💼</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="prizes-employment-title">Premios de Empleabilidad y Ecosistema</h3>
          <p class="prizes-employment-subtitle">Para el talento destacado — COCHATECH no solo premia proyectos, inserta talento real en el mercado laboral</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prizes-employment-grid">
        <div class="prizes-employment-card">
          <div class="prizes-employment-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🤝</div>
          <div class="prizes-employment-card-content">
            <h4 class="prizes-employment-card-title">Contratación Directa</h4>
            <p class="prizes-employment-card-text">
              Se abrirán <strong>2 puestos de trabajo formales</strong> para el área de desarrollo. Las empresas aliadas harán scouting en vivo durante el evento.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="prizes-employment-card">
          <div class="prizes-employment-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌟</div>
          <div class="prizes-employment-card-content">
            <h4 class="prizes-employment-card-title">Valor Profesional</h4>
            <p class="prizes-employment-card-text">
              Certificados virtuales de participación, acceso continuo a bootcamps de capacitación y entrada directa a la red de networking de alto nivel de Cochabamba y Bolivia.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Beneficios para Todos -->
    <div class="prizes-all-benefits" data-animate>
      <h3 class="prizes-all-benefits-title">Beneficios para Todos los Equipos</h3>
      <div class="prizes-benefits-grid">
        <div class="prizes-benefit-card">
          <div class="prizes-benefit-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">📜</div>
          <p class="prizes-benefit-card-text">Certificado oficial de participación</p>
        </div>
        <div class="prizes-benefit-card">
          <div class="prizes-benefit-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🤝</div>
          <p class="prizes-benefit-card-text">Acceso a la red de networking de alto nivel</p>
        </div>
        <div class="prizes-benefit-card">
          <div class="prizes-benefit-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">📚</div>
          <p class="prizes-benefit-card-text">Acceso a bootcamps de capacitación continua</p>
        </div>
        <div class="prizes-benefit-card">
          <div class="prizes-benefit-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">💼</div>
          <p class="prizes-benefit-card-text">Showcase en portfolio profesional</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .prizes-section {
    padding: var(--ds-space-16) clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    background: var(--ds-bg-elevated);
    font-family: var(--ds-font);
  }

  .prizes-container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Header */
  .prizes-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-16);
  }

  .prizes-title {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-2xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-8);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .prizes-accent {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ds-yellow), var(--ds-cyan));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .prizes-text {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-base);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 55ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-6);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  /* Featured Prize Card */
  .prizes-featured {
    background: var(--ds-glass-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-xl);
    padding: var(--ds-space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-16);
    transition: all var(--ds-t-normal);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .prizes-featured::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    right: -80px;
    top: -80px;
    width: 256px;
    height: 256px;
    background: var(--ds-yellow);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .prizes-featured-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--ds-space-10);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .prizes-featured-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .prizes-featured-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .prizes-featured-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--ds-yellow-dim);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.15);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-5);
  }

  .prizes-featured-title {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-4);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .prizes-featured-description {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-sm);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-6);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .prizes-benefits-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--ds-space-3);
    margin: var(--ds-space-6) 0 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .prizes-benefit-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--ds-space-4);
  }

  .prizes-benefit-icon {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .prizes-benefit-text {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .prizes-featured-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ds-glass-border);
    padding-top: var(--ds-space-6);
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .prizes-featured-right {
      border-top: none;
      border-left: 1px solid var(--ds-glass-border);
      padding-top: 0;
      padding-left: var(--ds-space-10);
    }
  }

  .prizes-value-label {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ds-text-muted);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-2);
  }

  .prizes-value-display {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--ds-yellow);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-6);
  }

  .prizes-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--ds-space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-6);
  }

  .prizes-featured-credit {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-xs);
    color: var(--ds-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .prizes-featured-credit strong {
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
  }

  /* Categories Grid */
  .prizes-categories-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-16);
  }

  .prizes-categories-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--ds-space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-4);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .prizes-categories-header {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
  }

  .prizes-categories-title {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-2xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .prizes-categories-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-sm);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--ds-space-10) 0;
  }

  .prizes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--ds-space-6);
  }

  .prizes-card {
    background: var(--ds-glass-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    border: 1px solid var(--ds-glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-xl);
    padding: var(--ds-space-8);
    transition: all var(--ds-t-normal);
  }

  .prizes-card:hover {
    background: var(--ds-glass-bg-hover);
    border-color: var(--ds-glass-border-hover);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--ds-shadow-lg);
  }

  .prizes-card-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-5);
    border: 1px solid;
    transition: transform var(--ds-t-normal);
  }

  .prizes-card:hover .prizes-card-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .prizes-icon-cyan {
    background: var(--ds-cyan-dim);
    color: var(--ds-cyan);
    border-color: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .prizes-icon-yellow {
    background: var(--ds-yellow-dim);
    color: var(--ds-yellow);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .prizes-icon-white {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .prizes-card-title {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-2);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .prizes-card-text {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-sm);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 var(--ds-space-4) 0;
  }

  .prizes-card-reward {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding-top: var(--ds-space-4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ds-glass-border);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .prizes-text-cyan { color: var(--ds-cyan); }
  .prizes-text-yellow { color: var(--ds-yellow); }
  .prizes-text-white { color: var(--ds-text-primary); }

  /* Employment Section */
  .prizes-employment-section {
    background: var(--ds-glass-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.15);
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-xl);
    padding: var(--ds-space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-16);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .prizes-employment-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -80px;
    bottom: -80px;
    width: 256px;
    height: 256px;
    background: var(--ds-cyan);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.07;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .prizes-employment-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--ds-space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-8);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .prizes-employment-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--ds-cyan-dim);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.15);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .prizes-employment-title {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--ds-space-2) 0;
  }

  .prizes-employment-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-sm);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .prizes-employment-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--ds-space-6);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .prizes-employment-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--ds-space-5);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid var(--ds-glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-lg);
    padding: var(--ds-space-6);
  }

  .prizes-employment-card-icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .prizes-employment-card-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .prizes-employment-card-title {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--ds-space-3) 0;
  }

  .prizes-employment-card-text {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-sm);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .prizes-employment-card-text strong {
    color: var(--ds-cyan);
  }

  /* All Benefits Section */
  .prizes-all-benefits {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .prizes-all-benefits-title {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-8);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .prizes-benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--ds-space-6);
  }

  .prizes-benefit-card {
    background: var(--ds-glass-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    border: 1px solid var(--ds-glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-xl);
    padding: var(--ds-space-6);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--ds-space-5);
    transition: all var(--ds-t-normal);
  }

  .prizes-benefit-card:hover {
    background: var(--ds-glass-bg-hover);
    border-color: var(--ds-glass-border-hover);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .prizes-benefit-card-icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .prizes-benefit-card-text {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-sm);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Design system badge styles (local fallback) */
  .ds-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-full);
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .ds-badge-yellow {
    background: var(--ds-yellow-dim);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.2);
    color: var(--ds-yellow);
  }

  .ds-badge-outline {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--ds-glass-border);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
  }

  .ds-badge-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ds-badge-dot-yellow { background: var(--ds-yellow); }
